籤詩版本二:
E hiahia ana ahau ki te kukume i te Immortal Gui ki roto i te Toad Palace, engari ka whakatuwheratia e ahau te kuwaha o te rangi ka tukua koe kia haere.
Inamata, kua pai te rongo, ka kata te katoa ki nga puawai o runga o te maunga
詩意:
Kei tenei hexagram te tohu o te osmanthus matekore.
Me noho rangatira i roto i nga mea katoa.
解曰: Nga painga o nga kaihokohoko. He (kaore) he kino ki te mau. Ka tau te mate, ka tau te whakawa. Mahia nga mea katoa ka taea e koe.
籤詩故事一:
◇Kia atawhai me te whai whakaaro
Ko Gao Huaide (926-982), ko Zangyong te ingoa, i whanau i Changshan, Zhending (inaianei ko Zhengding, Hebei).
I te wa o "Chenqiao Mutiny", na te mea i tautoko a Gao Huaide i a Zhao Kuangyin hei emepera, i whakanekehia ana ia hei kaititiro tuarua tuarua i mua i te whare rangatira.
I moe ano a Gao Huaide i te tuahine o Waiata Taizu Zhao Kuangyin (e rua nga tuahine a Zhao Kuangyin, i mate tetahi i te tamarikitanga, a, i muri iho ko te ingoa ko Princess Chen; ko tetahi i marenatia ki a Miford, engari kaore i mate tana tane, he pouaru ia inaianei. Ko Zhao Kuangyin te ingoa. Ko ia te kuini matamua o Yan). Ko te taitara rangatira ko Prince Consort Duwei.
(Ko te mea he toa taketake me te marena i te tuahine o te emepera, kaore he take e awangawanga ana mo te kore e whai mana.)
聖意: Kare te kainga i te ahua pai, he waimarie mo ia ano, he waimarie mo ia ano, he pai mo te pakihi, he aukati i te marena, he waimarie mo te hunga hikoi, he kino mo te mara. hiraka, e kore e pai mo te ono kararehe, e kore e pai mo te kimi tangata, he uaua te kimi tangata, he whakawa, he kino, he waimarie mo te heke, he waimarie, he. he waimarie, he waimarie, he mate, he maunga, he waimarie.
